[assistant]   "summary": "jackrabbit-webdav is a WebDAV client/server utility library whose artifact declares the Servlet API as provided; meaningful coverage of its normal server/request/response classes needs that API on the test classpath, but no external WebDAV server or Docker image is required for scaffold-level reachability coverage.",
